The paper also mentions the use of multi-view supervision, which could suggest that it belongs to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a novel approach for monocular dense human performance capture, which could suggest that it belongs to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
